The image is a black and white portrait of a woman with blonde hair. The caption on the image says "I will marry the guy that emails me when I block him."

The image is an Instagram post by @truebeauty.xoxo featuring a list titled "Red Flags You Missed Explained," which details various warning signs in relationships, such as overlapping relationships, maintaining contact with exes, and controlling behavior.

The image is an Instagram post by user "truebeauty.xoxo" featuring a quote about repeating patterns in relationships: "You'll keep meeting the same person in different bodies until you learn the lesson." The post has no comments yet.
